UI.SettingsUi.InfoNotif.Help:
The place wherein "Info" notices shall appear.
"Nowhere" shall show no Info notices
"Chat" shall print Info notices in chat
"Toast" shall show toast notices in the lower-right
"Both" shall show both chat and the toast notice

UI.SettingsUi.TransferWindow.Help:
The download window showeth the present progress of outstanding downloads.

What mean W/Q/P/D?
W = Waiting for a slot (see Maximum Parallel Downloads)
Q = Queued on the server, awaiting the ready signal
P = Processing the download (that is to say, downloading)
D = Decompressing the download
